    "summary": "<h2>2026.6.10</h2>\n<h3>Highlights</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Automatic fast mode for talks:</strong> OpenClaw can enable fast mode for short conversational turns, then return to normal mode for longer runs with bounded fallback and delivery behavior. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4498022958\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/85104\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/85104/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/85104\">#85104</a>) Thanks <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/alexph-dev/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/alexph-dev\">@alexph-dev</a> and <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/vincentkoc/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/vincentkoc\">@vincentkoc</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>More reliable model routing:</strong> Zai model synthesis, GLM overload failover, and native reasoning-level selection now follow the active model catalog more consistently. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4689768768\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94461\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94461/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94461\">#94461</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4664004790\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/93241\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/93241/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/93241\">#93241</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4681908533\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94067\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94067/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94067\">#94067</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4683210149\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94136\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94136/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94136\">#94136</a>) Thanks <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/Pandah97/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/Pandah97\">@Pandah97</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/chrysb/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/chrysb\">@chrysb</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/0xghost42/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/0xghost42\">@0xghost42</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/zhengli0922/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/zhengli0922\">@zhengli0922</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/openperf/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/openperf\">@openperf</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/civiltox/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/civiltox\">@civiltox</a>, and <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/BorClaw/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/BorClaw\">@BorClaw</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Safer session and channel state:</strong> channel switches reset stale origin fields, and cron delivery awareness stays attached to the target session. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4706639035\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/95328\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/95328/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/95328\">#95328</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4673056653\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/93580\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/93580/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/93580\">#93580</a>) Thanks <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/ZengWen-DT/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/ZengWen-DT\">@ZengWen-DT</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/jalehman/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/jalehman\">@jalehman</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/gorkem2020/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/gorkem2020\">@gorkem2020</a>, and <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/scotthuang/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/scotthuang\">@scotthuang</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Trusted policies survive hook composition:</strong> composed hook registries keep the trusted tool policies required by approval-sensitive flows. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4691598031\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94545\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94545/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94545\">#94545</a>) Thanks <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/jesse-merhi/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/jesse-merhi\">@jesse-merhi</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Changes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Agent and channel runtime:</strong> fast-mode state now survives retries, fallback transitions, progress events, and embedded/CLI/ACP normalization; session and channel routing retain the current target and delivery context. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4498022958\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/85104\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/85104/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/85104\">#85104</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4673056653\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/93580\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/93580/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/93580\">#93580</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4706639035\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/95328\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/95328/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/95328\">#95328</a>) Thanks <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/alexph-dev/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/alexph-dev\">@alexph-dev</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/vincentkoc/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/vincentkoc\">@vincentkoc</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/scotthuang/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/scotthuang\">@scotthuang</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/ZengWen-DT/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/ZengWen-DT\">@ZengWen-DT</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/jalehman/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/jalehman\">@jalehman</a>, and <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/gorkem2020/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/gorkem2020\">@gorkem2020</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Provider behavior:</strong> model catalogs now supply the correct Zai base URL, overload classification, and native reasoning controls for live-discovered models. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4689768768\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94461\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94461/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94461\">#94461</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4664004790\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/93241\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/93241/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/93241\">#93241</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4681908533\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94067\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94067/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94067\">#94067</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4683210149\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94136\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94136/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94136\">#94136</a>) Thanks