ost when hook registries are composed. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4498022958\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/85104\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/85104/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/85104\">#85104</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4691598031\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94545\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94545/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/94545\">#94545</a>) Thanks <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/alexph-dev/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/alexph-dev\">@alexph-dev</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/vincentkoc/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/vincentkoc\">@vincentkoc</a>, and <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/jesse-merhi/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/jesse-merhi\">@jesse-merhi</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Model and delivery edge cases:</strong> Zai and GLM failover paths use the right runtime metadata, while stale channel-origin state no longer leaks across session changes. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4689768768\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/94461\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_requ